<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edit Expense</title>

```
<link
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet"
>

<style>
    body{
        background: linear-gradient(135deg,#0d6efd,#6610f2);
        min-height:100vh;
        display:flex;
        justify-content:center;
        align-items:center;
    }

    .edit-card{
        width:600px;
        border:none;
        border-radius:20px;
        box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .card-title{
        font-weight:bold;
    }

    .logo{
        font-size:3rem;
    }
</style>
```

</head>

<body>

```
<div class="card edit-card">
    <div class="card-body p-5">

        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <div class="logo">✏️</div>

            <h2 class="card-title">
                Edit Expense
            </h2>

            <p class="text-muted">
                Update your expense details
            </p>
        </div>

        <form
            action="/updateExpense/<%= data._id %>?_method=PUT"
            method="POST"
        >

            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Title</label>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    name="title"
                    value="<%= data.title %>"
                    class="form-control"
                >
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Category</label>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    name="category"
                    value="<%= data.category %>"
                    class="form-control"
                >
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Amount</label>
                <input
                    type="number"
                    name="amount"
                    value="<%= data.amount %>"
                    class="form-control"
                >
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Date</label>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    name="date"
                    value="<%= data.date %>"
                    class="form-control"
                >
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <label class="form-label">Description</label>
                <textarea
                    name="desc"
                    class="form-control"
                    rows="3"
                ><%= data.desc %></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="d-grid gap-2">

                <button
                    type="submit"
                    class="btn btn-primary"
                >
                    Update Expense
                </button>

                <a
                    href="/dashboard"
                    class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
                >
                    Cancel
                </a>

            </div>

        </form>

    </div>
</div>
```

</body>
</html>
